					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The only thing I know of is writing to $4003/$4007 every frame. You should only write to those regs when the value changes. It isn't the case for the triangle, I believe (you should be able to write to $400B every frame). Also, you want to write to $4003/$4007 if you disable/re-enable the square waves via $4015.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/" class="postlink">-Owner of Poultry Games</a></div>
