				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">My sound effects are made of code, not data. Each one is so unique that code gives more flexibility than a universal handler that's fed data. Though you could make a universal routine that's fed data, it would take lots of data to define the sound you want. And when you think of it, code given a chunk of RAM can do A LOT.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/" class="postlink">-Owner of Poultry Games</a></div>
